---
title: Pesto Chicken Quesadillas with Balsamic Baby Leaf Salad
description: Sandwiched together with a pesto chicken filling and plenty of cheese, these Pesto Chicken Quesadillas are a fusion favourite combining Italian flavours and an easy Mexican inspired dinner.
